    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_2",
    "text": "1.地球水球",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11343561134356113,
      0.2119118130964133,
      0.2798698279869828,
      0.23362948338269168
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_3",
    "text": "(1)地球表面陆地面积占29%.海洋面积占71%.概括为“七分海洋，三分陆地” (2)分布：陆地主要集中在北半球，海洋主要集中在南半球.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1413296141329614,
      0.24086870681145114,
      0.9177126917712691,
      0.2948338269167489
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_4",
    "text": "2.十大洲和四大洋 (1)关于海洋陆地的基本概念：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11064621106462111,
      0.3376110562685094,
      0.3263598326359833,
      0.35867061533399147
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_5",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14318921431892143,
      0.36722606120434353,
      0.4686192468619247,
      0.3882856202698256
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_6",
    "text": "地域 概念 大洲 大陆和它附近的鸟屿 大陆 面积广大的陆地 岛屿 面积较小的陆地 洋 海洋的中心部分",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1394700139470014,
      0.3902599539322145,
      0.7215248721524872,
      0.5429417571569596
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_7",
    "text": "是洋的一部分.位于大洋辺缘，面积较小.靠近大陆 沟通两个海洋之间的狭窄水道",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.26313342631334263,
      0.5521553142481079,
      0.7131566713156672,
      0.6061204343534057
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_8",
    "text": "(2)海陆分布大势：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16271501627150162,
      0.6186245475485357,
      0.34309623430962344,
      0.6416584402764067
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_9",
    "text": "①六块大陆：亚欧大陆、非洲大陆、南极大旺、澳大到亚大陆，北美大陆、南美大陆 ②七大洲：亚洲：非洲：北美洲、南美州：南极洲、欧州·大洋洲 ③四大洋：太平洋.大西洋.印度洋、北冰洋",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.18781961878196188,
      0.6475814412635735,
      0.9270106927010693,
      0.7337940111878908
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_10",
    "text": "④大洲分界线：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1896792189679219,
      0.7443237907206318,
      0.34309623430962344,
      0.7653833497861139
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_11",
    "text": "亚.欧：乌拉尔山脉写拉尔河→里海→大高加索山脉—→思 海—→土耳其海陕(沟通黑海和地中海）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.198977219897722,
      0.7706482395524844,
      0.9446768944676894,
